CreateNoticeboardCommunicationObject
public class AgentCommunicationObject
extends java.lang.Object

A simple object that brings together information about the communication between agents and services. This is used to update the controller and the agent in turn after being modified. If a Question is set, then statement is expected to be the answer to this statement;
